#summary The juror decides that the match ended

{{{
do_juror_end_match(finished_player_ids:Array/*int*/, scores:Array/*int*/, pot_percentages:Array/*int*/)
}}}

In [ClientGameAPI], all players had to call [do_agree_on_match_over] to end the match.
In [SecureClientGameAPI], only the juror have to call [do_juror_end_match] to end the match.
The arguments of the two functions are identical and explained in [do_agree_on_match_over].
